|1 |└─PX COORDINATOR                          |        |2       |1472        |
|2 |  └─EXCHANGE OUT DISTR                    |:EX10001|2       |1472        |
|3 |    └─MERGE GROUP BY                      |        |2       |1471        |
|4 |      └─SUBPLAN SCAN                      |tmp_t   |1500    |1457        |
|5 |        └─WINDOW FUNCTION                 |        |1500    |1455        |
|6 |          └─SORT                          |        |1500    |917         |
|7 |            └─EXCHANGE IN DISTR           |        |1500    |780         |
|8 |              └─EXCHANGE OUT DISTR (RANGE)|:EX10000|1500    |551         |
